      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments completed by a second analyst.",
      "rationale": "A second FEA engineer independently reviewed boundary condition assignments, contact pair definitions, and material property inputs against the simulation plan. No discrepancies identified. Use error risk is low."
