      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Linear elastic with bilinear plasticity model validated against material coupon data; contact formulation consistent with ASTM F1717 fixture geometry.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity with Ti-6Al-4V coupon-derived parameters (E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa, tangent modulus=2.1 GPa). Contact between screw head and rod modeled with augmented Lagrange formulation. Model form is appropriate for the quasi-static bending regime."
